nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values: medium close-up shot, slow motion, pull-back, underlighting, magic effects, saturated colors, cinematic, surreal, futuristic, surprised, pensive.The shot begins as a medium close-up, intimately framing the girls' faces. The moment they finish the scroll, the entire sequence unfolds in breathtaking slow motion. An intense, surreal light erupts from the altar below, casting dramatic underlighting that illuminates their features. Their faces are a cinematic canvas of emotion—first shock and surprise, which then softens into a profound, pensive look of understanding and epiphany. Shimmering magic effects, like a cascade of stardust, swirl and rise around them, their hair and clothes gently lifting from an unseen force. As the light crescendos, the camera begins a slow pull-back. The ancient chamber dissolves into the brilliant white, and as the light recedes, it unveils a completely new world: a surreal, futuristic landscape of impossible floating structures and flora pulsing with saturated colors. The two girls now stand as small figures against a vast, unknown backdrop, their grandest adventure just beginning.
